searchPerson(String) - Method in class server.PartyPlannerService
Method used to retrieve certain Users (Person object) that meet the criteria defined by the @PathParam("smth"); It references the ModelManager object to execute the command and retrieve the result which is sent back to the HttpClient using the web service provided; The result is either a List in case favorable or null in case the procedure failed and was aborted
searchPersonBySmth(Package) - Method in class server.DatabaseConnectionTier2
Calls createSockets() in preparation to sending a Package command; Sends out the package using the ObjectOutputStream variable; The method waits for the result List which it received using the ObjectInputStream variable; The socket connection is closed and the result is being returned.
searchPersonBySomething(String) - Method in class server.ModelManager
Method used in retrieving users that met a specific criteria specified by the parameter; A Package object is being created with the command "searchPBySmth" and the parameter is being added/attached to the Package; It then refers to the DatabaseConnectionTier2 variable that transmits the Package command for execution.
